Managing Director of CHI Limited, Mr. Roy Deepanjan, has expressed delight with the feedback received so far from consumers regarding the recently-introduced Hollandia Evap 120g pack size better known as “Pere”. “At the price point of N100, we were confident that the Hollandia Evap 120g “Pere” pack was good value for consumer spend when making purchasing decisions. The convenient portion size and affordability is driving affinity and growing popularity of the pack size amongst consumers desirous of wholesome nutritious milk,” Deepanjan said at a recent press parley. With the Hollandia Evaporated Milk 120g pack size joining the 190g and 60g pack sizes on the shelf, and is now available in departmental stores across the country, consumers are commending the company for another pack of the wholesome nutritious evaporated milk. At N100, millions of consumers have become endeared to “Pere” across Nigeria for its unique creamy taste and nourishing value in a convenient pack as it is tailored to fit specific consumer needs with quantity benefits. Among consumers who spoke, Mr. Oluseyi Adeniyi, a Brand Consultant with MarketingPlus, said: “The Hollandia Evap 120g “Pere” pack size is an innovative pack that offers a good on-shelf presentation and delivers fresh appeal in addition to its creamy goodness. The pack’s increasing popularity is driven by consumer trends and desire for convenient portion size, more personal choice and affordability.” Also, Ezekiel Usman, a student of University of Ibadan, said Hollandia Evap is a creamy and highly nutritious milk that has also has a pocket friendly pack. “Each day, I always take a hot cup of coffee or a bowl of cereal complemented with Hollandia Evap because of its freshness, creamy goodness and vital nourishment. Now with the N100 “Pere” pack, I am glad I still get the same great taste, nutrition and satisfaction at an affordable price,” he added.